headline: Kroger Fuels Protein Goals with Expanded Simple Truth™ Line Now Featuring More Than 110 Items
summary: With the new year officially underway, The Kroger Co. (NYSE: KR) is making it even easier for customers to focus on building healthy protein habits. Adding 24 new affordable, flavor-forward and protein-packed Simple Truth™ Protein products to shelves this month, the retailer has expanded the line to 110+ offerings – all Free From unwanted ingredients and designed to support any nutrition goal, from establishing new everyday habits to building strength.

headline: Ocado hit by fresh warehouse closure as North American partners cut ties
summary: Ocado has been hit by a fresh setback in its North American business after its Canadian partner decided to shut one of its robotic warehouses.
